@startuml
title Chatbot RAG + Groq - Vue simplifiee

skinparam shadowing false
actor "Utilisateur" as User
participant "Angular" as Front
participant "API Spring Boot" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Groq API" as Groq

User -> Front : Question
Front -> API : POST /api/chat
API -> DB : Construire contexte RAG
DB --> API : Donnees financieres
API -> Groq : Prompt + contexte
Groq --> API : Reponse IA
API --> Front : Reponse
Front --> User : Affichage
@enduml
